							Amidst the pandemic, Klaus Oegerli, a Swiss tourism industry
							veteran was deeply concerned that many friends in his network
							were out of work, while the need for information soared. Under
							what conditions can I go where? Expertise was sought but
							everybody wanted it for free.<br> <br> Klaus gave this
							problem some thought and decided to launch a consumer to consumer
							platform, offering paid video consultation by all kinds of travel
